        "jsCode": "// Loop over input items and add a new field called 'myNewField' to the JSON of each one\nlet result=[];\nfor (const item of $input.all()) {\n  let temp=JSON.parse(item.json.data);\n  console.log(temp)\n  \n let orderDetails=temp.orderDetail.details.map(el=>{\n    return {\n      sku_code:el.sku_code,\n      sku_name:el.sku_name,\n      quantity:el.qty,\n    }\n  })\n  //将sn和uuid分开存放在不同的数组中\n\n  result.push({\n    platform_code:temp.orderDetail.platform_code,\n    orderDetails:orderDetails\n  })\n}\n\nreturn result;"
